snippet.title: CONCLUSE - FINAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
CONCLUSE will be released JUNE 29th on STEAM.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/826230/CONCLUSE/

Winners of the early soundtrack raffle:

VFXNinja
DarkSpartan765
Monika Just
H u l k a r o n i & C h e e s e
Givaldo Onides


If you won, send an email to conclusevideogame@gmail.com and I'll send you your code for an early soundtrack download.

Otherwise, the soundtrack releases for FREE on June 21st

Want to pre-order the Concluse soundtrack and support the artists? Here are a few links:

Spotify: https://bit.ly/2J2VNuI
Amazon: https://amzn.to/2J99KDD
Itunes: https://apple.co/2JmZuuJ
Google Play: https://bit.ly/2HaNwze
Steam: https://bit.ly/2syomVY
